e D8-120 Cabrio</a> sold for $940,000 in 2022, while the car below apparently <a href="https://www.classic.com/m/delahaye/135/year-1937/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">did not sell</a> ).</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315334" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="453" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3-300x189.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3-1024x645.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3-768x483.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3-250x157.jpeg 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-3-1536x967.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315335" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="453" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2-300x189.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2-1024x645.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2-768x483.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2-250x157.jpeg 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-2-1536x967.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/4-2.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315336" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/4-2.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="453" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-con